{"tid":1550597,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該你要上最前線既話自我審查下係唔係左膠先","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:45:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T03:01:27.000Z","uid":254123,"like":60,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ed3e940743de0db9c11e3cac653c9a46920eb2ed","tid":1550597,"uid":254123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:45:52.000Z","msg":"唔該你地上前線時問下自己以下幾個問題！<br />\n<br />\n1. 真係有衝突你會唔會頭也不回咁走？ <br />\n會 》咪再企咁前<br />\n<br />\n2. 有人打你你會唔會還手？   <br />\n唔會 》咪再企咁前<br />\n<br />\n3. 有黑社會/藍絲搞事你會唔會幫手制服？<br />\n唔會 》咪再企咁前<br />\n<br />\n4. 開緊波你會唔會做和事佬/禁住自己人？   <br />\n會 》 咪撚再企咁前<br />\n<br />\n唔係話割蓆， 左膠同和理非係唔同既種類既人，唔好混為一談。<br />\n<br />\n左膠心中只有光環，不必要既仁慈，即係偽善，自我滿足。<br />\n<br />\n因為當黑警真係衝黎捉人時佢地一定第一時間唔見人， 因為佢地夠膽阻既，只有仁慈既示威者。因為佢地知道手足們唔會傷害佢地，係自己絕對安全既情況下放膽咁阻止自己人，甚至間接/直接令人畀人拉。<br />\n<br />\n左膠們甚至連自己係幫兇都唔清楚！"},{"pid":"bf5eb20c8f19d831271d47c560cb66d5d408d062","tid":1550597,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:46:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51f6a2037074852b27a141e32ffcbbeac58ebf0c","tid":1550597,"uid":172290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:48:24.000Z","msg":"屌你老母有左膠都算，搵人禁住佢咪俾佢阻撚住晒得唔得"},{"pid":"d2787dc274e21980cad45ea7050a093f7173c1c3","tid":1550597,"uid":254123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51f6a2037074852b27a141e32ffcbbeac58ebf0c","tid":1550597,"uid":172290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:48:24.000Z","msg":"屌你老母有左膠都算，搵人禁住佢咪俾佢阻撚住晒得唔得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:51:25.000Z","msg":"如果未出手點會有人知邊個係左膠丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n肯出黎係好事，但真係要自我審查下，搵個適合自己既位置。"},{"pid":"86a10a5687a1ae84a9a018e4492284710b0a4b3e","tid":1550597,"uid":254123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:54:55.000Z","msg":"放心，如果有人不幸被拉，我地一定支持到底，直到無條件釋放所有人為止！"},{"pid":"8804378135a63f6f742b556f2be74095e7e304c6","tid":1550597,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:55:26.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我警告你班仆街！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽日啲<span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國旗</span>唔好周圍掉！<br />\n路邊見到唔該即刻幫手執返！<br />\n完咗活動攞返屋企收藏！</span></span><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evxvjtB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevxvjtB.jpg&h=73325a8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 快啲聽熟加背歌詞，<br />\n唱得莊嚴啲！</span>\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC6dOOFpqpiAZGwRsEzlRJXk%3D&h=9aa24d7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n分段背易啲背：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Oh, say can you see,</span></span><br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">What so proudly we hailed,</span><br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Whose broad stripes and bright stars,</span><br />\nThrough the perilous fight,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">O'er the ramparts we watched,</span><br />\nWere so gallantly streaming.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">And the rocket's red glare,</span><br />\nThe bombs bursting in air,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Gave proof through the night,</span><br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Oh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,</span><br />\n<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave.</div><br />\n<br />\n聽日見！</span>"},{"pid":"777eaa2f9cde57f0398c29fdb34fed5a6df0c6ec","tid":1550597,"uid":254123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:56:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c9be0e19c99256e8f0b72cb8e2d3dde09bc28d5","tid":1550597,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:57:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"37f1dac0a45daecb138a0ced5a698bd8c8584ea7","tid":1550597,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7744116b27c585ea5ec4638304f557a75a67ac6","tid":1550597,"uid":261895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:03:28.000Z","msg":"你第一條問題已經考到好多前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"175bbd642aec847d39aa7c1ff08c90388c383222","tid":1550597,"