意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"9212e56912f66dce76683089723a26133245b0b1","tid":1550597,"uid":254123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:33:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">開遮拉膠</span></span>"},{"pid":"9f9b91f58e4567dc2b71fd57f3e16e087a17740c","tid":1550597,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:42:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c778f6216c8b9e933ad1c9548502867c87a4e436","tid":1550597,"uid":67425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T21:34:13.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"ec1b86f1cc385566a176584e155f735fe3b27441","tid":1550597,"uid":67425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T21:35:13.000Z","msg":"點解要咁夜出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52e6cd80afc584dad40b89ec68d18127c47f0af","tid":1550597,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T22:19:18.000Z","msg":"不受傷不被捕呢兩句口號係比和理非<br />\n唔係比勇武派架<br />\n如果各位勇武抱著呢兩句口號行動<br />\n拜託你唔好再做勇武<br />\n去做和理非算了<br />\n<br />\n每次一聽到有狗<br />\n就落荒而逃<br />\n我地人多勢眾<br />\n但同警犬對抗的勇氣都冇<br />\n有手捉被捕就扮作視而不見<br />\n雞飛狗走<br />\n勇武兩個字的武字<br />\n根本從來冇展現過出黎<br />\n何來自稱勇武派？<br />\n大家充其量只是死物破壞者，塗鴉者，建設路障者，掉磚者和掉雞尾酒者而已。<br />\n<br />\n勇武前線的口號應該係<br />\n不怕受傷不怕被補<br />\n怯的話<br />\n請回頭做和理非<br />\n但不要少看和理非<br />\n和理非也有其威力的"},{"pid":"87e998a233997414c9ee32848c22b77f4a100e4c","tid":1550597,"uid":254123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec1b86f1cc385566a176584e155f735fe3b27441","tid":1550597,"uid":67425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T21:35:13.000Z","msg":"點解要咁夜出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:59:17.000Z","msg":"點訓得著丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgm